BlankApplication Extension SalesForce Connector
==========

BA Extension SalesForce is a plugin to handle remote connection to SalesForce
Of course, You need to have an activated account on SalesForce.com with a personnal key associated.
This plugin let you configure an SalesForce Connection

Dependencies
=======

This plugin is based on activerecord-activesalesforce-adapter gem distributed on http://github.com/luigi/activerecord-activesalesforce-adapter
just run: sudo gem install activerecord-activesalesforce-adapter

Install
=======

Simply run:
rake salesforce:install

